Package: panna
Title: Player Rating System for Football Using RAPM and SPM Methods
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Pete", "Owen", , "pete.owen1@hotmail.co.uk", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Implements player ratings for football (soccer) using
    Regularized Adjusted Plus-Minus ('RAPM') combined with Statistical
    Plus-Minus ('SPM') as a Bayesian prior. Analyses time segments with
    constant lineups ('splints') to estimate each player's contribution to
    expected goals ('xG') differential. Provides offensive and defensive
    rating decomposition across multiple data sources including 'FBref',
    'Opta', and 'Understat'.
